@startuml
hide footbox
actor "Admin" as Admin
boundary "DepartmentListPage.jsx" as ListUI
control "api.js" as FrontendAPI
control "departments_api" as API
entity "PhongBan" as DB

Admin -> ListUI: Click icon "Xóa"
activate ListUI

ListUI -> FrontendAPI: GET Check Employee Count
activate FrontendAPI
FrontendAPI -> API: Request đếm NV
activate API
API -> DB: Count Employees
activate DB
DB --> API: Count
deactivate DB
API --> FrontendAPI: {employee_count}
deactivate API
FrontendAPI --> ListUI: Count
deactivate FrontendAPI

alt Có nhân viên (Count > 0)
    ListUI --> Admin: Cảnh báo "Không thể xóa"
else Trống (Count = 0)
    ListUI --> Admin: Hộp thoại xác nhận xóa?
    
    Admin -> ListUI: Xác nhận (Đồng ý)
    ListUI -> FrontendAPI: DELETE /api/departments/{id}/
    activate FrontendAPI
    FrontendAPI -> API: Request xóa
    activate API
    
    API -> DB: Delete Department
    activate DB
    DB --> API: Success
    deactivate DB
    
    API --> FrontendAPI: {success: true}
    deactivate API
    FrontendAPI --> ListUI: Success
    deactivate FrontendAPI
    
    ListUI --> ListUI: Reload danh sách
    ListUI --> Admin: Thông báo thành công
end

deactivate ListUI

@enduml
